To compile:

./configure
make
make install


The executable is copied in the bin folder
To test the code copy the executable in the EXAMPLES folder and:

./MAMMA

A Matlab script (plot_solution.m) is provided in the PLOTTING_SCRIPTS folder to plot the results.



This work has been partially supported by the Marie Curie Actions of the European Commission in the frame of the MAMMA project (FP7-PEOPLE-2009-IOF-251833)

